1. Introduction

MorseGenie is a simple utility bot designed to translate text between English and Morse code.
This Privacy Policy explains what data the bot collects, how it is used, and how your privacy is protected.

2. Information We Collect

MorseGenie does NOT collect, store, or process any personal data outside Zoho Cliq.
Specifically:

‚úî Data the bot handles:

Messages you send to the bot

Text or Morse input you provide

‚úî Where the data stays:

All data remains inside Zoho Cliq servers, as part of normal bot operation.

The bot does not transfer data to external servers, databases, or third-party APIs.

‚ùå MorseGenie does NOT collect:

Your name

Email address

Contact details

Files or media

Usage analytics

Login information

Any identifiable personal data

3. How Collected Data Is Used

Messages sent to MorseGenie are used only to perform translations:

English ‚Üí Morse

Morse ‚Üí English

No data is used for tracking, profiling, marketing, or any secondary purpose.

4. Data Storage & Retention

The bot does not store any data permanently.

All user inputs exist only during the active session handled by Zoho Cliq.

Once processed, the data is discarded automatically.

5. Data Sharing & Third Parties

MorseGenie does not share data with:

Third-party companies

External servers

Advertisers

Analytics tools

Your inputs are never shared or sold to anyone.

6. Security

MorseGenie relies on Zoho Cliq‚Äôs secure infrastructure.
There is:

No external database

No external API

No external data transmission

This minimizes security risks and keeps your information fully protected within your organization.

7. User Rights

Since no data is stored, you do not need to request deletion or correction.
However, if you have concerns, you may disable or remove the bot at any time.

8. Changes to This Policy

If this Privacy Policy is updated, the new version will be published at the same URL.
Continued use of MorseGenie after updates means you accept the revised terms.

9. Contact

For any questions or clarifications regarding privacy, please contact the bot developer through your Zoho Cliq organization.
